<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29886>
    dc:description "Figures 35 - 39. Pulaeus illustrations. 35 Genital setae in a row 36 - 39 Pulaeus key illustrations 36, 37 Venter, setae removed for clairity 36 a Coxae I-II not coalesced medially, median platelet present 36 b Coxae I-II not coalesced medially, median platelet absent 37 a Coxae I-II coalesced medially, median platelet present 37 b Coxae I-II coalesced medially, median platelet absent 38 a Dorsal shield with punctures 38 b Dorsal shield with broken striae 39 a-c Pedipalp tibiotarsus 39 a Tibiotarsus with elongate apophysis 39 b Tibiotarsus with flat apophysis 39 c Tibiotarsus with flange-like apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29886" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

